        [
          "Staff Generated History"
        ],
        [
          "From a very young age you have watched as others who were better off got everything, at least from your persepcctive. You wanted what you felt was owed to you. You didn't come from a bad family, but you always wanted more. So after high school you applied to the best schools you knew you could get into with sschlarship and you did. While there you moved among the more well-off students and made fast friends. Mostly by doing things they couldn't or that would get them in trouble. You gained a reputation for getting things done and you loved it. You felt you were on your way up. Then one night while out fullfilling a request you met your would be sire. She said she had been watching you for some time. She apprecitated how you made a name for youself. She also said she knew the truth about you and needed to show you more. The Embrace left you more then a little unhindged, but you knew you saw the REAL inner workings of the world. You could see the gears spin. And then you understood...if you can see how the machine works, you can use it to fullfil your dream and rise to the top of your new society."
        ],
